dct_title_s: Tracks of H.M. vessels in search of the Eight Stones
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. "1763." A survey by vessels ordered by the Admiralty to locate rocks in the Atlantic north of Madeira which were alleged to be dangerous; the tracks are labeled with dates from 1825 to 1842.
